{
  "stem": "26486.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "For what-- the little-- I knew her long time, but I didn't know too much of her family background.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But I know that she had a daughter.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "She had been married.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "She had a daughter that was about-- when I knew her, about-- she must have been about 14-- about Jenny's age-- that I met after.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "She was married to a-- I think he was from the Flanders.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He was from a very good family from the Flan-- but anyway.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They didn't get along.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And she divorced.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And she had the daughter.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "That's as much as I know of her family.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I know she became a very good friend of mine.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And after the war, we stayed very good friends.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Pardon me?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we didn't even see-- she wasn't with me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We worked for the underground together, but she wasn't where I was.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "As a parachuter, they sent her everywhere.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She was in the north of France.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She was in the south of France.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Anywhere where the Germans could be, they sent her.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And she spoke several languages too.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then as I told you, one day, she was coming down in the north of France, in a parachute.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And a German shot at her.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And the bullet went in back of her heart.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And in her back, came out under her heart.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And she killed him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And then the-- the farmers-- it was in the country-- took it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Thank you.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "The farmers came and rescued her.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And they took care for her.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They sent her probably-- I don't know where-- where she was.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But anyway, I met her when I was in Ravensbruck.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Somebody came.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And they called me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And they said, Mick, Mick!",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Somebody you know!",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Somebody you know!",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Come and see!",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "It's your daughter!",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Oh my heaven.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
